snippet.title: Sat Yoga Institute
snippet.description:
This channel is an introductory portal into the transformational teachings of Shunyamurti.

Subscribe to our YouTube channel and three weekly uploads, including satsang teachings, questions and answers and guided meditations.

Sat Yoga Institute, based in Costa Rica, is an ashram, retreat center, and spiritual community, guided by the profound teachings and presence of Shunyamurti. It is a place to study, to heal, to meditate, it is a place to realize your highest potential.

Stay connected - Join our newsletter - http://eepurl.com/dPEt7z

For information about our retreats and long term study programs, please visit our website www.satyoga.org

SHUNYAMURTI: https://www.satyoga.org/shunyamurti

MEMBERS SECTION
Gain unlimited access to an extraordinary and ever-growing collection of Shunyamurti's advanced teachings. 
Sign up for your free 10-day trial: https://www.members.satyoga.org/
